			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just killed the Lava Elemental today for the Power of Fire (although my gnomie faction hurts a little for it), and it took me awhile to get the proper PH's to spawn.<br>
<br />

<br />
There is a Clockwork that wanders in the hallway outside the lava room that you must kill before the PH inside the lava room spawns (a few minutes later, and it's another clockwork).  One you have the PH inside the Lava Room, you can keep killing him until the Lava Elemental spawns and (hopefully) drops your Power of Fire piece.  There are 5 regular clockwork spawns in the room, but only one spawn (the PH), will spawn halfway between the pillars and wander around the room.  The whole zone is on a 19 minute spawn timer, so this is a good place to go when you have to do laundry, cook, eat, clean house, etc and don't want to be tied down with the intensities of a regular group or raid.  This, of course, is assuming that you have good gnome faction and the whole place doesn't crash in you!<br>
<br />

<br />
Enjoy!<br>
<br />

<br />
Frex,<br></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
