				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">On Firiona Vie, you may have to plan your outings to avoid getting stung by the Trivial Loot Code.  The upside is that there are not many NO DROP items, so you *may* be able to find some of the now-trivial items on sale in the Bazaar.  However, with the lower server population and one-character-per-account limit, not many people go to older zones where a lot of the lower level items drop (e.g. Najena...I'm having a heck of a time getting the Torn Pages of Mastery since the Magicians are green).</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
