				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">On Firiona Vie, the mobs that con green present a real problem to those attempting quests and epics because of the Trivial Loot Code.
<br />

<br />
The easiest way around this is to go into raid with someone...anyone - their level doesn't matter.  Most people try to use a bazaar mule - either their own or a guildmates.  Or you can try hollering in PoK or the Bazaar.  Most understand how frustrating the TLC can be and are willing to accomodate.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
